{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"AgentSight","page":{"layout":"document","title":"AgentSight 故障排查","description":"事件缺失、TLS hook 失败和 UI 问题的常见处理方法。","descriptionIsExcerpt":false,"bodyHtml":"<p>这一页覆盖本地运行 AgentSight 时最常见的问题。</p>\n<h2 id=\"目标进程没有出现\">目标进程没有出现</h2>\n<p>先确认 command name 是否匹配真实进程名：</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">ps</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -eo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> pid,comm,args</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\"> |</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\"> grep</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -E</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> 'claude|node|python'</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>然后把 <code>comm</code> 列中的值传给 AgentSight：</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./agentsight</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> record</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -c</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> node</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"缺少-tls-event\">缺少 TLS event</h2>\n<p>可能原因：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>目标进程使用的 TLS 库与当前 probe 预期不同。</li>\n<li>Runtime 静态打包了 OpenSSL。</li>\n<li>真正发起网络请求的不是被 trace 的进程。</li>\n<li>流量经过了另一个未被 trace 的 proxy 进程。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果 Node.js binary path 明确，可以尝试：</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./agentsight</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> record</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> --binary-path</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /usr/bin/node</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -c</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> node</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"权限错误\">权限错误</h2>\n<p>使用 root 权限运行 AgentSight，并确认 host 允许加载 eBPF 程序。一些限制严格的 container、kernel 或 security profile 会阻止所需操作。</p>\n<h2 id=\"ui-无法打开\">UI 无法打开</h2>\n<p>确认本地 server 正在运行，且 <code>8080</code> 端口没有被其他进程占用：</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">ss</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -ltnp</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\"> |</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\"> grep</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> 8080</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>如果端口已被占用，停止对应进程；如果当前 build 支持，也可以配置 AgentSight 使用其他端口。</p>\n<h2 id=\"event-太多\">event 太多</h2>\n<p>尽量缩小目标进程范围，并在可行时加入 analyzer filter。对于敏感 session，应在 recording 前减少 capture scope，而不是只依赖事后脱敏。</p>\n<h2 id=\"数据顺序看起来不对\">数据顺序看起来不对</h2>\n<p>比较事件时优先使用 collector 规范化后的 timestamp。原始 kernel、userspace 和 frontend timestamp 可能因 buffering 或 clock source 不同而有差异。</p>","headings":[{"id":"目标进程没有出现","text":"目标进程没有出现","depth":2},{"id":"缺少-tls-event","text":"缺少 TLS event","depth":2},{"id":"权限错误","text":"权限错误","depth":2},{"id":"ui-无法打开","text":"UI 无法打开","depth":2},{"id":"event-太多","text":"event 太多","depth":2},{"id":"数据顺序看起来不对","text":"数据顺序看起来不对","depth":2}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/agentsight/troubleshooting.zh.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2026-06-02T03:15:25.000Z","createdAt":"2026-06-02T03:15:25.000Z","authors":[{"name":"LinuxDev9002","email":"linuxdev8883@example.com"}]},"path":"/zh/agentsight/troubleshooting/","alternates":{"en":"/agentsight/troubleshooting/","zh":"/zh/agentsight/troubleshooting/"},"continuation":{"index":{"title":"AgentSight","description":"基于 eBPF 的 LLM 与 AI agent 零插桩可观测工具。","href":"/zh/agentsight/"},"previous":{"title":"AgentSight 快速开始","description":"安装 AgentSight，记录一个 agent 进程，并在本地 UI 中查看 session。","href":"/zh/agentsight/quickstart/"},"next":{"title":"AgentSight 可视化","description":"如何阅读 AgentSight UI，并把事件关联成一个 agent session。","href":"/zh/agentsight/visualization/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"AgentSight","items":[{"title":"总览","href":"/zh/agentsight/"},{"title":"快速开始","href":"/zh/agentsight/quickstart/"},{"title":"架构","href":"/zh/agentsight/architecture/"},{"title":"可视化","href":"/zh/agentsight/visualization/"},{"title":"运行说明","href":"/zh/agentsight/operational-notes/"},{"title":"故障排查","href":"/zh/agentsight/troubleshooting/"}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}